OL,3,COverground line reopens four days
OL,4,Cafter major Walthamstow fire
OL,6,FThe Weaver Line, on the London
OL,7,FOverground has reopened four days
OL,8,Fafter it was partially suspended
OL,9,Fbecause of a major Walthamstow fire.
OL,11,FAround 125 firefighters battled the
OL,12,Fmajor blaze in Walthamstow after a
OL,13,Frailway embankment caught fire on
OL,14,FSunday evening.
OL,16,FAt its height, the fire could be seen
OL,17,Fraging metres from railway lines as it
OL,18,Fspread to homes and around 30 gardens.
