OL,3,COverground line reopens four days
OL,4,Cafter major Walthamstow fire
OL,6,FFive days on and the Weaver line is
OL,7,Fback in action, according to Transport
OL,8,Ffor London, although it is operating
OL,9,Fwith minor delays.
OL,11,FWatch: Fire engulfs a garden in
OL,12,FWalthamstow
OL,14,FThe fire left two families homeless,
OL,15,Fand St Mary's Church in Walthamstow
OL,16,Fhave raised #7500 so far to support
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
