OL,3,COverground line reopens four days
OL,4,Cafter major Walthamstow fire
OL,6,FIn the churches online appeal, they
OL,7,Fsaid: "The two households lost
OL,8,Feverything when the fire ripped
OL,9,Fthrough their flats."
OL,11,FIt continued that the families "will
OL,12,Flikely face many months of being
OL,13,Fhomeless as well as having to start
OL,14,Fagain".
OL,16,FSt Mary's and Ghousia Grove Road Hall
OL,17,Fboth welcomed in hundreds of people
OL,18,Fwho were forced to evacuate their
OL,19,Fhomes on Sunday.
